        <div class="div-welcome">
          <h1>Welcome</h1>
          <p>Founded in 1985 by Shari, Garen, Brandon and Shannon, Staglin Family Vineyard takes pride in the tradition of family ownership and participation. With an uncompromising commitment to quality, our mission is to produce world class wines that reflect the distinctive character of this historic Rutherford Bench estate. As stewards of this land we farm the vineyard organically, tap in to our solar fields for power and produce the wines in a state of the art underground production facility.
            <br>
            <br>We are passionate about this business, this land, our philanthropy and for the meaningful relationships we develop with each passing day. We hope this passion is evident when you enjoy our wines.</p>
